Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.41,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}想想你是從哪裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如何走到了今日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:07.96,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}失敗!!
